(44135, 139447, 0, 1, 'Don''t Turn Away From Me (Demo Version)', 'Just a love song.', '2012-03-31 00:00:00', 2012, 0, 1, 7, 'Since the day I was born I knew I was meant to be yours.\r\nSince the day I was born I knew I was made for you.\r\nSince the day I was born I knew I was born to watch over you.\r\nUntil I found you.\r\n\r\nBut the reality, brought the gravity, crave the scars on our skin.\r\nThe sweet memories, and the bad one we had, babe can we just choose to forgive?\r\nThose days of silence, the words of violence,\r\nwhy do we have to be so mean?\r\nOh lord, please, I will give you anything.\r\n\r\nBut don''t you turn away from me.\r\ndon''t you turn away from me.\r\nRemembering you said that you will never let me go,\r\nand why are you walking away from me?\r\n\r\nTime is never enough for you to spend sometime with me.\r\nTime is never enough for me to spend sometime with you.\r\nThe reasons are never good enough to ignore the mistakes we made in the past.\r\nAnd see now, that''s how we failed.\r\n\r\nBut don''t you turn away from me,\r\ndon''t you turn away from me.\r\nRemembering I said that I will never let you go \r\nso why are you walking away from me, now?\r\n\r\nWhere are you, going?\r\n\r\nHow are you, doing?\r\nWhat were you, before?\r\nWhat are you?\r\n\r\nDon''t you turn away from me.\r\nDon''t you turn away form me.\r\nRemembering the day you told me you will never let me go,\r\nbut why are you walking away from me?\r\n\r\nDon''t you turn away from me.\r\nDon''t you turn away from me.\r\nRemembering the day you told me we''re gonna have everything.\r\nBut why are you walking away from me, now?\r\nWhy do you walk away from me? \r\n', '', 262, '', 'Bix Song', 'Bix Song', 'Bix Song', 'No label', '', 0, 0, 1, '2012-03-05 04:16:25', '2013-10-07 17:20:30', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
