(44138, 122400, 0, 1, 'Warm Winter', 'My initial cowrite with Devon for Berklee''s "Sonwriting Collaboration" class.\r\n這學期在berklee修一門課 - project #1', '2012-03-04 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 7, 'It was forty some degrees down by the river\r\nThe ice was taking cover in the ground\r\nRunning from the sound of tug of war\r\nBetween the willow and the wind\r\nSo the story begins, as I remember\r\nWhen I came across a blossom in a December\r\n\r\nSilhouette was fading with the sunrise\r\nRevealing hints of red and simple peach\r\nThe colors that would teach my eyes to open\r\nAnd see the life that sat still \r\nWith the breath so strong it warmed me like an ember\r\nWhen I came across a blossom in December\r\n\r\nShe looked me into the eyes like it was nothing\r\nSlowing let her breath turn into words\r\nShe spoke of how the morning was her garden \r\nGiving birth to everyday\r\nUntil it burned out with the sun reduced to cinder\r\nWell though winter blew it away\r\nWhen I came across a blossom in December\r\nIn December..in December..in December.. ', '', 175, '', 'Devon Yesberger & Stacy Huang', 'Devon Yesberger & Stacy Huang', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2012-03-05 06:59:30', '2015-03-12 13:50:47', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(44139, 72723, 0, 1, '棉十(上)The Truth 配唱草稿-所有聲音未處理', '寫詞人殘葉（自理名言）臉書連結：https://www.facebook.com/windjack.cheng/info\r\n作曲人王彰駿臉書連結：https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100000303234475&sk=info', '2012-03-05 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 7, '<The Truth>\r\n詞：殘葉 2012/01/30\r\n曲：王彰駿2012/02/21\r\n\r\n(副歌)\r\nI HATE MYSELF\r\nI HATE EVERYTHING ABOUT...THE TRUTH.\r\n這世間所有虛幻的事物　他們說　孩子你～不可碰觸！\r\n\r\n(主歌1)\r\n我尋夢踏上　音樂的旅程\r\n管他前程坎坷顛簸　似乎荊棘滿佈\r\n管他離經叛道　荒廢公式　矯情做作又粗俗\r\n我仍滿懷希望　躍進那鍋大雜燴裡　光鮮亮麗的烹煮\r\n\r\n(副歌)\r\nI HATE MYSELF.\r\nI HATE EVERYTHING ABOUT...THE TRUTH.\r\n這世間所有虛幻的事物　他們說　孩子你～不可碰觸！\r\n\r\nI HATE MYSELF.\r\nI HATE EVERYTHING ABOUT...THE TRUTH.\r\n這世間所有虛幻的事物　他們說　孩子你～不可碰觸！\r\n\r\n(Rap)\r\n孩子啊～孩子　你要牢牢的記住\r\n寧願沉重肩上的抱負　也不要磨損了你的意志\r\n勇氣就像活躍的音符　可恥的是那裝作胡塗的一臉無辜\r\n\r\n(橋段)\r\nBECAUSE......BECAUSE......THE TRUTH......IS\r\nFACE YOURSELF.才是　真的　幸福～\r\n\r\n（FACE YOURSELFｘ４）\r\n\r\nI HATE MYSELF,I HATE MYSELF\r\n\r\n(Rap)\r\n孩子啊～孩子　你要牢牢的記住\r\n寧願沉重肩上的抱負　也不要磨損了你的意志\r\n勇氣就像活躍的音符　可恥的是那裝作胡塗的一臉無辜\r\n\r\n(橋段)\r\nBECAUSE......BECAUSE......THE TRUTH......IS\r\nFACE YOURSELF.才是　真的　幸福～\r\n\r\n(轉調)\r\n轉眼時光飛逝我～衣衫襤褸　一如當初\r\n這才明白好逸惡勞　大放厥辭　任性耍酷根本無法～風雨無阻\r\n\r\n\r\n但是　他們忘記了　有一種屈服叫做　過份保護\r\n懦弱正如塵垢蔓延　斜倚牆角吉他癱瘓了樂譜\r\n我的一生荒蕪　無法給你留下　任何　光榮名目\r\n於是　懸殊　殘酷　沉澱　凝固成我　心酸的全部\r\n', '', 191, '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 1, '2012-03-05 07:56:15', '2013-10-07 17:20:30', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
